from Imam Reza (a) that if any person recites YAA BAARE-O 100 times during daytime then Allah (swt) will not leave him alone in the grave but will give him a helper and a partner.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a.s) se manqool hai keh jo shakhs Juma ke din 100 martaba YAA BAARE-O ka vird karega to Khuda wande aalam us ko qabr mein tanha nahin rehne dega bal-keh us ka ek moonis (madad gaar) o saathi qaraar dega.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ جو شخص جمعہ کے دن 100 مرتبہ ’’یَا بَارِیُٔ‘‘  کا ورد کرے گا تو خداوندعالم اس کو قبر میں تنہا نہ رہنے دے گا بلکہ اس کا ایک مونس و ساتھی قرار دے گا۔ ", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "Arabi